						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 993, Virōdhikṛit, Uttarāyaṇa-saṅkrānti,</hi> corresponding probably to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1078 December 25.</hi> Details are not enough for verification. It refers itself to the reign of the Chāḷukya king <hi rend="bold">Tribhuvanamalladēva</hi> and records the grant of some land for the service of the god Mallikārjunadēva of <hi rend="bold">Koṇḍakunde.</hi> </p>						

